Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little while longer, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:33.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥方様、もう少しにござりまするぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, be strong. \NYour child will be here any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:39.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥方様、お気を確かに…もう少しにござりまする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Daigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐様か…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One who steps into this Hall of Hell \Nhas made a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:42.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地獄堂へ入られたということは、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To cast off Buddha and the gods \Nin favor of the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:46.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神仏を捨てこの鬼神たちに…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it is futile to try and stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:51.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もはやお止めすることはできますまいな…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But hear me one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう一度だけ言うておきましょう…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:00.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐様…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:05.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御仏の道を外れるは外道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To cast off Buddha is to tread \Nthe path of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,外道にあるは人にあらず…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It is to no longer be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cross this line, \Nhell will surely await you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:14.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,踏み出せば、この先あなた様を待っているのはただ地獄…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest, we are already living in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:18.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,上人殿…地獄とはこの世のことよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:24.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたらが日がな一日拝んでいた御仏の道など、どこにもありはせぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The holy path to Buddha you pray for \Nexists nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You will pay the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では…どうあっても…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知れたこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I care not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがたき…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これで救われまする…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be my salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is indeed hell, \Njust as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:52.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今の世は地獄…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,日々祈りは空しゅう…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The prayers I offered \Nseemed more and more pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:03.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いずれ我がうちに御仏への疑いが生まれるやもと…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I always feared that some day \NI would begin to doubt Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その前に死ぬるは何より…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad to die before that day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Daigo, please stay away \Nfrom the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:13.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐様…鬼神に近づいてはなりませぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let yourself succumb to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:18.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きながら外道に堕ちては…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう…堕ちておる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:31.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,12の鬼神に言う！我が名は醍醐景光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,12 Demons, I am Daigo Kagemitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord of Ishikawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,加賀国守護者、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:38.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,富樫政親様の配下にしてこの石川領領主である
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and vassal to the governor of Kaga Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeated famines and epidemics \Nhave swept my land,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:43.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,度重なる飢饉と流行り病によって、我が領土の民、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死を待つばかりに痩せ衰えた…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,enfeebling my people to the point of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:54.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このままでは生涯の望み…我が名を天下に轟かせることなど、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As things stand, I shall never attain \Nthe power and renown I crave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My ambitions will remain a mere dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,夢のまた夢なり…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I refuse to rely on the mercy of \NBuddha or the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:02.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが！神仏にすがろうとは思わぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:06.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これから申すこと、そなたらへの祈りではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What I am about to say to you \Nis not a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,取引である！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:13.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もし我が領土を守護し、我に天下を握らせるならば…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll protect my land \Nand let me rule the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それより他に、我が手に入るものをやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you anything of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything. Take whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:22.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいか、何でもだ！そなたたちの好きなものを取るがいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返答やいかに！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:42.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥方様…もう少し…もう少しにて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:46.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,南無観世音菩薩…ご加護を…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddess of Mercy, please protect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おほほ、生まれましたぞ！おほほほほ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,如何した！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:18.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the baby born?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生まれたのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが… \N-何だ！ハッキリいたせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, but... \N-What? Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿…生まれました…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He is born, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,男の子にございまする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He is your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御方様… \N-世継ぎか、でかしたぞ奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-My lady... \N-An heir, you've done well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿、お待ちを！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何事が起こったのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:47.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んではおりませんが、手足どころか目も鼻も
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He is alive, but has no limbs, \Neyes, nor a nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,皮膚もなくなってしまいました…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have any skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you anything of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手に入るものをやろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything. Take whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:57.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何でもだ！そなたたちの好きなものを取るがいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:03.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿、わたくしは儚く愛おしいと思いました…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I feel a deep love \Nfor this woeful child of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:08.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どのような姿であろうとも、間違いなく殿とわたくしの子にございます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter his appearance, he is our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream will be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,叶ったぞ…これで我が望みは叶った！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿！ \N-鬼神が取引に応じたのだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-My lord? \N-The demons agreed to the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,案ずることはない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくぞ生んでくれた…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bearing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうするのです！その子をどこへ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait! \N-Forget him. He never even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:36.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待って！ \N-忘れよ…あれは初めからいなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいえ！いいえ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥方様！まだ起き上がってはなりませぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, you mustn't get up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿、お慈悲を！あの子を…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奥…！あれではどうせ長くは生きられぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't survive anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならば尚の事…我が胸で…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let him pass away in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい加減にいたせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤子はまた生まれよう、いや生んでもらわなくてはならん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will bear another child. You must.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天下の世継ぎとなろうからな…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one will be \Nthe heir of a great ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,先程、雷が落ちたときに弾け飛んで…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was blown away \Nwhen the lightning struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,産婆は、何かの身代わりではないかと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The midwife said it sacrificed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身代わり？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I’m gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it’s not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it’s not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. I’m gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. I’m gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,#1 The story of Daigo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何の因果か知らぬが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever could've caused this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これでは、生きてるほうが地獄だろうて…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, being alive \Nwould only be harder for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go on dear. \NBuddha will take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:40.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ…あの世で仏様に拾っておもらい…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:47.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だろうかね…こんなことは慣れっこのはずだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be used \Nto this sort of thing by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…生きたいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you desire to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:16.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あとは…お前さんの運次第だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to your luck, dear boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,臭うねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:38.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こりゃあ…悪さの臭いだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The stench of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人ともつかぬ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、あやかしでもない…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, not a ghoul, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何やら因果な臭いだねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:27.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,加賀国ざかいにある醍醐景光の領地は、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo Kagemitsu's land \Nat the border of Kaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:34.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,度重なる飢饉を乗り越え、繁栄の一歩を辿り始めたこの日…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After overcoming many famines, \Nit was on its way to prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:39.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,泣き声さえ上げられぬ小さな命の塊が、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the tiny soul, \Ntoo weak to even let out a cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人知れず消えていったことを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly vanished off into obscurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:47.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領民の誰1人知る者はなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There was none in the land \Nwho knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,16 YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この頃、戦は常にどこかで起こり、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, there was always a war \Nbeing fought somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:57.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人の命は石ころのように転がっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Human lives were hardly worth \Nmore than a stone on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ…もし、お前さま。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:20.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さまが、近頃仏に失った手足をつけて弔っているというお医者か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the doctor who gives prosthetics \Nto the dead to mourn for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,寿海とか申される
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Jukai, am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まことに、ご奇特な…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:32.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…ただの試作したものを捨てるよりはと思っただけのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured it'd be better \Nthan throwing away the prototypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも、仏は喜びましょう…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure they are grateful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:04.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ、とっくり見てってくれ！どれもこれも都の極上品だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come, take a look. \NQuality goods, straight from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:09.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら！この着物は貴族のお姫様が着ていた本物の絹。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is real silk. \NA wealthy princess wore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お姉さん、触ってみなって！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come miss, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:17.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっと、この壺はなんとあのヤマタノオロチの酒ガメだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a sake jug from \Nthe Yamata no Orochi legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他じゃ手に入らない掘り出し物ばかり！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All one-of-a-kind quality items.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,安くしとくよ！買ってくれたら、この干し魚もおまけにつけちゃう！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a bargain. \NI'll even throw in these dried fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ、早いもん勝ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,げ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見つけたぜどろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:39.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつは俺たちが運んでいたもんだなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the load we were carrying, \Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこにそんな証拠があんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:47.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やかましい！腹減って死にそうだってぇから、\N荷物番に雇ってやりゃあコレだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You said you were starving, \Nso we hired you to look after our goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞けば、あちこちで似たようなことやらかしてるそうじゃねぇか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your usual trick, we hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大したタマだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You little rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見つけたらこらしめてくれって頼まれちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guys asked me to make sure \Nyou paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハッ…このご時世、子供だからって油断するほうがマヌケなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for being so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勉強になったろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should learn from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ。だからもう手加減はしねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, no more nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大人と同じ仕置きを受けてもらうぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this, just like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待てこのガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you little brat! Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前らみたいなウスノロに捕まるかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:22.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ちやがれ！このクソガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get back here, dammit! \N-We'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すいませんねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、ボーっとしてないでちゃんとお礼言いな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん、今日お祭り？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a festival today, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何言ってんの、こないだ終わったばっかだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. \NWe just had one not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だって…あの兄ちゃんお面つけてた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But he had a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソッ…どこ行きやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！臭ぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,馬フンだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Horse manure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wash your faces with those, \Nand come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asking for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad about that load though. \NThat was good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. I'll just go for the next fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Can't find your mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You hungry? Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't. You have to learn \Nhow to live on your own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn how to find your own food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mine now, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let go of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he yours? \NThen he'll pay for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it. \N-Then do what we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Had enough? Don't you ever steal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-You brat! \N-You asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Never show your face here again, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody orders me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose where I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me that straw mat. \NI'm wrapping him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, there's some weird guy up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a face like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes too. Where's he looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not some bullies, you know. \NWe're the ones being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think he's looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's looking behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's nothing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just some floating garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It ate him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face. Those eyes, \Nears and all are fake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't hear, can ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to walk a step \Nwith my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But you run and jump \Nwithout using a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Your skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hunted a turtledove for you. \NIt will make you strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Tahomaru, will cook it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It rained like this that day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you human?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Deiki"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつでツラ洗って出直してきな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇいもう勘弁ならねぇ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ…面白かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けどあの荷物は残念だったな、上物だったのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、また次のマヌケを狙うか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:27.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だ？お前。おっかちゃんとはぐれたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腹減ってんのか？しょうがねぇな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:36.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや、ダメだ。お前はこれから1人で生きてかなきゃなんねぇんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,甘やかしちゃ、お前のためになんねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人に頼らず自分で取ってくるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメダメ、お前のために言ってるんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう逃さねぇぜどろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイ！そいつ離せ！離せよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:59.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつお前のか？だったらお前の代わりに痛い目見てもらおうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ！\Nじゃあ大人しくしな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:16.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これで懲りたろう！二度と悪さすんじゃねぇぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このガキ！\N-まだ足んねぇのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もういい…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:31.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっさとこの町から出て行けよ…いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:35.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い…嫌だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらは誰の指図も受けねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこにいようとおいらの勝手だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなに死にてぇか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,望み通りにしてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:59.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイ！そこのムシロ持ってこい！簀巻きにしてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイ！何やってんだ、早くしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:13.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親方…なんか気味悪ぃヤツが…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:15.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの顔…人形みてぇだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目ン玉もだよ…どこ見てんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かに気味悪ぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイ兄ちゃん！なんか文句あんのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:33.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちがガキいじめてると思ったら大間違いだぜ！\Nいじめられたのはこっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オイ！聞こえてんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ…やんのか兄ちゃん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:43.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う…あいつが見てんの、多分俺たちじゃねぇよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの目…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たち通り越して、後ろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何だよ、後ろなんか誰もいねぇよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:11.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何でぇ、ゴミが流れてきただけじゃねぇか…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食われ…ちまった？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの兄ちゃん、化け物見てねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハハッ…すげぇ、すげぇよ兄ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:04.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ…あんたのその顔、目も耳も作りもんだよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで周りが分かんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:10.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…その耳じゃ聞こえないんだろうけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ…おいら目を閉じたら怖くて1歩も歩けねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのに兄ちゃんは杖もなしに走ったり飛んだり！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一体どうなってんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え…？なんで…どうしたんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怪我したのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…何だよ、これ！顔の皮が…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,"HALL OF HELL"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:15.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま…まさか…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山鳩を仕留めて参りました！精がつきますぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この多宝丸が調理いたしまする！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:37.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは楽しみな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの日も、こんな雨だった…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊や…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:08.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,顔…顔が…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ…？どうなってんだよ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた…何なんだ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:16.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人間なのかよ！？
